Date: Thu, 9 Apr 2026 22:03:28 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 13/16] port: Refine and isolate Android/Termux build logic

Cleans up the initial Termux port by safely walling off mobile-specific workarounds.

- Wrapped X11, EGL, and V4L2 hacks in strict __ANDROID__ macros.
- Cleaned up CMake using generator expressions for Android linking.
- Renamed mobile telemetry to system-info-android.cpp.
